Package org.framed.orm.ui.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExpandStateChangeCommand
    Through this command the model attribute isExpand from type model elements can be changed.
    FulfillRolesCommand
    This command is used from the FulfillRolesAction and the RolesDialog to add all the names of the choosen RoleGroups and RoleTypes to the fulfilledRoles list of a Fulfillment and delete all the names of the not choosen RoleGroups and RoleTypes from the fulfilledRoles list of a Fulfillment.
    ORMAddCommand  
    ORMCloneCommand  
    ORMOrphanChildCommand  
    ORMRoleModelCreateCommand
    Through this command the model element Rolemodel can be created(invoked into the model tree).
    StepCommand
    This command realize the step in/out, which is initialized by the StepInAction, the StepInNewPageAction, the StepInNewTabAction or the StepOutAction, through changing the content of the viewer of the ORMMultiPageEditor instance, which owns the Compartment or the Grouping the user wants to step in/out.
